OL,3,CMan knocked out at Preston bus stop in
OL,4,Crow over parenting
OL,6,FA 'well intentioned' passerby stepped
OL,7,Fin to resolve a parenting row at a
OL,8,FPreston bus stop - but then knocked
OL,9,Fout a man and stamped on his head.
OL,11,FJoseph Robinson approached the person
OL,12,Fafter becoming aware of an argument
OL,13,Fabout a child in November last year, a
OL,14,Fcourt heard.
