OL,3,CMan knocked out at Preston bus stop in
OL,4,Crow over parenting
OL,6,FSalek Ahmed, prosecuting, told Preston
OL,7,FCrown Court that the 33-year-old
OL,8,Fbelieved the man had been demanding a
OL,9,Fmember of the public 'slap their
OL,10,Fchild'. Robinson intervened but the
OL,11,Frow quickly escalated and he punched
OL,12,Fthe man who then hit his head on a
OL,13,Fbench.
OL,15,FAs he lay unconscious on the floor,
OL,16,FRobinson then stamped on his head and
OL,17,Fneck, leaving him surrounded by a pool
OL,18,Fof blood.
