OL,3,CMan knocked out at Preston bus stop in
OL,4,Crow over parenting
OL,6,FWitnesses fled the attack in fear and
OL,7,Fpolice were flagged down on Garstang
OL,8,FRoad. Robinson remained at the scene
OL,9,Fasking if he had killed him, the court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe victim was taken to hospital and
OL,13,Ftreated in intensive care for multiple
OL,14,Ffractures to his face, cheekbone and
OL,15,Fleft eye socket.
OL,17,FAnthony Parkinson, defending, called
OL,18,FRobinson's assault 'short lived' and
OL,19,F'spontaneous' and said the victim's
OL,20,Ffractures did not require any invasive
OL,21,Fprocedures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
