OL,3,CMan knocked out at Preston bus stop in
OL,4,Crow over parenting
OL,6,FHe added: "There is no excuse for it
OL,7,Fbut he didn't carry out an assault for
OL,8,Fno reason. His intentions were
OL,9,Finitially good."
OL,11,FRobinson, of Robinson Street, Preston,
OL,12,Fhas struggled with a heroin addiction
OL,13,Fsince the age of 18 and was
OL,14,Fintoxicated at the time of the attack.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to Section 20 GBH
OL,16,Fwithout intent at an earlier hearing.
OL,18,FThe court heard that Robinson's father
OL,19,Fkilled his mother when he was a child
OL,20,Fand that this disturbing crime had a
OL,21,Fprofound impact on his life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
