OL,6,FBut the judge in the case said
OL,7,FRobinson's criminal past - with 47
OL,8,Fseparate offences listed - was an
OL,9,F'alarming record of his violence'.
OL,11,FJailing him for 30 months, KC Graham
OL,12,FKnowles said: "The defendant remained
OL,13,Fat the scene asking if he had killed
OL,14,Fhim and made other remarks which are
OL,15,Fcompelling proof he is a guilty man.
OL,17,F"Obviously the victim was vulnerable
OL,18,Fwhen you stamped on him. The risk was
OL,19,Fvery serious indeed, the risk of
OL,20,Fdamaging his spinal cord, paralysis is
OL,21,Fall there.
